title: Who's too high? Who's too low? Breaking down the College Playoff Rankings plus Sonny Dykes and a Class of 2024 Commitment
description:
The crew looks into the College Football Playoff initial rankings, discussing who missed out and who made it to the 4 playoff spots, who was disrespected and who was overrated, and the three first-time-ranked teams. Additionally, the crew touches on the four Michigan State players who were suspended for their involvement in the tunnel altercation with Michigan this past weekend. Uncommitted Class of 2024 dual-threat quarterback Julian Sayin joins the show live for decision between LSU, Georgia, and Alabama. Then, Sonny Dykes then joins to discuss TCU's undefeated season and their number 7 CFP ranking.
